description:
Anna, Sim, and Lena chat with two callers in need of advice…

…Juliana confessed her romantic feelings to John, a guy in her close friend group, and was gently turned down - but after finding out that John’s roommate has had feelings for her, Juliana now wonders if John was just hiding his true feelings for her to honor the bro-code?

…Ariana has always had a difficult relationship with her older sister which is why she finds herself in a dilemma now that she’s getting married. Ariana needs help deciding if she should invite her sister to the wedding and risk ruining her big day or not invite her sister and potentially regret that decision forever.

Visit unqualified.com/contact to share your thoughts or send us your relationship questions – we can’t wait to hear from you!
